snippet.title: Jann Dhan Mann: Patiala's Opinion on PM Modi's Demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000

localized.description:
Jann Dhan Mann: Patiala's opinion on PM Modi's demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes. Watch India TV's special report to know what people of Patiala thinks about note ban and its affect on upcoming assembly elections in Punjab.
